item.title: CVE-2021-37216|2024-08-04T01:16:03.944Z -- qsan -- storage%20manager%20xn8008t
item.description: QSAN Storage Manager header page parameters does not filter special characters. Remote attackers can inject JavaScript without logging in and launch reflected XSS attacks to access and modify specific data.
